Apple uses HTTP Live Streaming protocol. VLC should be able to play it just fine. You will probably need a custom URL to feed VLC though. I&#x27;ll paste the URL here once it&#x27;s available.<p>EDIT: Quick bash script for extracting VLC-playable URLs (when they&#x27;re available):<p><pre><code>    curl `curl http://www.apple.com/apple-events/september-2013/ | grep &quot;p.events-delivery.apple.com&quot; | sed &#x27;s/\<script.*src=&quot;\(.*\)&quot;.*/\1/&#x27; | sed &#x27;s/&quot;.*//g&#x27;` | sed -e &#x27;s/[ \t]//&#x27;
</code></pre>
